Fritz Von Erich https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fritz_Von_Erich 0 Jack Barton Adkisson Sr. (August 16, 1929 – September 10, 1997) was an American professional wrestler known more under the ring name Fritz Von Erich, better known today as a wrestling promoter and the patriarch of the Von Erich family. He was also the owner of the World Class Championship Wrestling territory.
